formula_15

where the relation between the angular frequency and angular wave vector is given by the dispersion relation:
formula_16
such that formula_17. This relation should be valid so that the plane wave is a solution to the wave equation. As the relation is &quot;linear&quot;, the wave equation is said to be non-dispersive.

To simplify, consider the one-dimensional wave equation with . Then the general solution is
